divs: Sighting DetailsWatching in my back yard an UFO that has whit flashing lights under it. Red and green on top. Seems to be hovering over Robstown.
Summary: Watching what looks like a star, moving up and down for about 30 min. Still observing.
trends: There have been 2 other sightings in Robstown
